---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 文章归档
description: Zinc Acetate 的算法题解、比赛复盘、训练记录与站点日志。
permalink: /archive/index.html
---
<section class="page-heading">
  <div class="page-width">
    <p class="overline"><span aria-hidden="true"></span> WRITING / ARCHIVE</p>
    <h1>文章归档</h1>
    <p>题解、复盘与训练过程中留下的笔记。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="archive-section">
  <div class="page-width archive-layout">
    <div class="archive-index">
      <span>{{ collections.blogPosts.length }}</span>
      <p>ARTICLES<br>AND COUNTING</p>
    </div>
    <div class="post-list archive-list">
{% for post in collections.blogPosts %}
        <article class="post-row">
          <div class="post-date">
            <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDate }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
            <span>{{ post.data.category }}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="post-summary">
            <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
            <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
          </div>
          <div class="post-read">
            <span>{{ post.data.readingTime }}</span>
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" aria-label="阅读《{{ post.data.title }}》">
              <i data-lucide="arrow-up-right" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            </a>
          </div>
        </article>
{% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
